&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Success in this role is measured by procurement execution excellence, supplier delivery performance, material availability, ERP data integrity, and the effectiveness of the Buyer organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
