&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Strong programming skills in Python, with proficiency in deep learning frameworks such as PyTorch.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with modern learning-from-demonstration tools like DiffusionPolicy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with robot data collection, training, and testing on hardware to perform manipulation tasks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to work collaboratively in a fast-paced environment to deliver safe, high-quality software&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;MS in Robotics, Computer Science, or a related field.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
