&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain template agreements, playbooks, and negotiation guidelines to scale the contracting process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
